snippet.title: Gindama Oyakata no Pachinko Hisshouhou Intro for Super Famicom
snippet.description: It's the amazing Japanese Pachinko, now on the Super Famicom.  I imagine the real thing would be a little more fun.  Kind of like playing a casino game on the Nintendo here, yes it functions and winning is totally possible, but there's no money, so....
